Build:

```bash
rm -rf dist/ tdspu.egg-info/
python setup.py sdist bdist_wheel
python -m twine upload dist/*
cd conda
rm -rf tdspu
conda skeleton pypi tdspu
conda build tdspu
# anaconda upload TARBZ
```

Conventions:
  - Every ZFS dataset contains the directories: data, ncmls

Examples CMIP6:

```bash
find data -type f -regextype egrep \( -regex '.*_fx_.*' -o -regex '.*_Amon_.*' \) | ncmlify --project cmip6 --root $(pwd)/data --ncmls ncmls2 --aggregation 'project,activity_id,institution_id,source_id,experiment_id,variant_label,grid_label'
```
